main event: A round, silver object was sighted straight up through the window of a car for one minute.
interesting points: The object was very bright and moved very fast in a straight up direction.
The sighting occurred in the northeast direction from the witness's location.
The object faded out after one minute of observation.
The witness was a USAF controller at the nearby Sea-Tac Airport.
The sighting was initially thought to be an aircraft, but was later concluded as probably being an aircraft.
